txt.en: Defeat Black Númenórean soldiers in Parth Daenath ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Black Númenóreans can be found in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should defeat Black Númenórean soldiers and their captains.
Bounty: Black Númenóreans in Parth Daenath
A bounty notice asks you to push back the Black Númenórean's advance in Parth Daenath.

You have defeated Black Númenórean soldiers and their captains, successfully pushing back their assaults in Parth Daenath. The man who posted the bounty will be pleased that the Great Alliance has been made safer, and if he truly manages to refrain from gambling on the makeup of the enemy forces, his coin-purse should not get much lighter.

The bounty notice reads:\n\n'After so many years of siege, our forces are spread thin, and every now and again there are fresh assaults at the locations we are weakest! I would wager all of my coin that it's these Black Númenóreans who are responsible. Take up the sword and put a stop to these attacks, because my purse runs low. I need to stop making these wagers!'
